1537	  triple-overlap chart ring \(R_{IJK} := \mathrm{Localization.Away}\,(P^I_J\cdot P^I_K)\)
1538	  the composite ring endomorphism
1539	  \[
1540	    \Phi := \Theta_{I,J,K} \circ \mathrm{swap}_J \circ \Theta_{J,K,I} \circ \mathrm{swap}_K
1541	            \circ \Theta_{K,I,J} \circ \mathrm{swap}_I
1542	  \]
