2041	  % is `IsTerminal.hom_ext`), the morphism-form `isSeparatedToSpecZ` (a direct port of
2042	  % `AlgebraicGeometry.Proj.isSeparated`: per-patch closed immersion from `diagonalRingMap_surjective`
2043	  % via `IsClosedImmersion.spec_of_surjective`, source iso `pullbackιIso`, two-leg `pullback.hom_ext`),
